description: Looking for a neighborhood that is close to retail shopping, restaurants and more, well here it is.  Wonderful schools and close to everything. Popular Avalon floor plan with formal living and dining rooms, large foyer, PLUS an office downstairs with French doors. The kitchen area has an EXTRA LARGE ISLAND with granite countertops, nice sized pantry, tons of cabinets, desk area and great DOUBLE WALL OVENS. Refrigerator, Washer and dryer are also conveying! The breakfast area has lots of windows... could be a FLORIDA ROOM/ AREA. The open floor plan is great for entertaining with the columns separating the flow from kitchen, breakfast, to great room. Nice sized walk in laundry room is also on first level. 2 sets of stairs leads you to the second floor where there are 3 bedrooms PLUS the Master Suite and the OVERSIZED BONUS/ MEDIA ROOM (with closet, so could be another bedroom - #5). The master is so spacious and the master bath has his/ hers walk in closets as well as HIS/HER SINK AND VANITY AREAS. Great value for this square footage, features and location.  Schedule your appointment today.

description: Fabulous home on two lots in Colleton Park. This is a 2 story move in ready home with 4 Bedrooms, 3.5 Baths, plus a large Bonus Room ( 387 sqft). There are beautiful wood floors throughout the first floor, stairs, and upstairs hallway. The home has a formal dining room, a large family room with cathedral ceilings and electric fireplace and has access to a screened porch. The kitchen has granite countertops and stainless appliances, a snack bar and breakfast nook. Off the kitchen is the pantry and coffee station. The large master bedroom is on the main floor and the master bath has a garden tub, large tiled shower and vanity with granite. Upstairs there are three guest bedrooms, two full baths and bonus room. The home comes with an extra lot that is fenced and includes a large outdoor kitchen, dining area, firepit and has plenty of room for a vegetable garden!  Rear entry two car garage .
